<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Kenya's data.<br />Open and accessible.</h1>
    <p>Data about Kenya is buried in PDFs, messy Excel files, poorly documented, and hard to access. Getting it ready for analysis or development is a headache. +254 extracts data from Kenyan institutions, cleans and processes it, and serves it through a plug-and-play API.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="/datasets/" class="btn-primary">Explore data <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      <a href="/api-docs/" class="btn-secondary">API docs <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero-text {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-warm-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: 0;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    hyphens: none;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-regular);
    color: var(--color-warm-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 62ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .hero-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-primary,
  .hero-btns .btn-secondary {
    min-width: 140px;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-green);
    transition: background-color 0.2s var(--ease-out), color 0.2s var(--ease-out), transform 0.15s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-primary:active,
  .hero-btns .btn-secondary:active {
    transform: translateY(1px);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-primary:focus-visible,
  .hero-btns .btn-secondary:focus-visible,
  .hero-btns .btn-ghost:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid #fff;
    outline-offset: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--color-green);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-ghost {
    min-width: 140px;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1.5px solid transparent;
    color: var(--color-warm-light);
    transition: color 0.2s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .hero-btns .btn-ghost:hover {
    color: var(--color-warm-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: var(--space-xs) 0 var(--space-lg);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
